author: Amai Ta. Yume
text:
Thank you everyone again for the whole some stream. I like to take more focus on the Super chat reading. It got better and better than before by the way. A lot of people are now from around the world trying to thank Rushia and it feels very wholesome! Thank you JP and EN bros for every support that you have! No matter how little or how much you give, even just by watching and liking the video, it's something that will help Rushia in the long run.

For Rushia, Thank you for doing your best as usual. I believe you'll be more fantastic than before. Just do what you love to do and I'm here supporting you with everyone! I hope you had a good time today because we had tons of fun! <3 

Oh and Redan! waiting for the season finale. Give it a bang!
